{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"324f266d1d","title":"大字报——进行曲","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"b886f68606","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":null,"articleId":"324f266d1d"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"4e38dc5cec","name":"西北师范学院"},{"id":"bf263e5a33","name":"易水"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"48b1abaf3d","type":"title","text":"大字报——进行曲","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"c560f7ba21","type":"authors","text":"西北师范学院易水","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"8e609d2d10","type":"paragraph","text":"党棍专权，恶风猖狂！","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"8612d8ef08","type":"paragraph","text":"恶以益恶，坏得不成模样！","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"94f3622573","type":"paragraph","text":"从这儿向全国胆望：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"edee7dd3d8","type":"paragraph","text":"到处都堆积着奇形怪象。非法的行为披上合法的伪装！","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"528d71c950","type":"paragraph","text":"是则聪慧何济于人心，","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"e408881b0f","type":"paragraph","text":"慈爱何济于人情，","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"38a07cd37d","type":"paragraph","text":"敏捷何济于伎两，","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"15607774f4","type":"paragraph","text":"唯真唯一的精神何能发挥力量！","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"100b4d57b0","type":"paragraph","text":"到头来一个正人君子，","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"6cb490337b","type":"paragraph","text":"全变成奸佞流氓！","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"bb3a1af9f5","type":"paragraph","text":"这样社会只好分崩离析，","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"5034c995b7","type":"paragraph","text":"闹到是非颠倒，公道沦亡！","index":13,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"5d54e9e696","type":"paragraph","text":"可是因此而愤怒的群众，","index":14,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"0c3c8c6447","type":"paragraph","text":"愈来愈加激昂！","index":15,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"e41358a9c2","type":"paragraph","text":"挺身呐喊，有如狂涛猛浪！","index":16,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"7d20c66378","type":"paragraph","text":"同学们！我们也是这巨流中的一分力量，","index":17,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"88f4627dff","type":"paragraph","text":"我们要顽强斗争，使这个邪恶的制度改变模样！","index":18,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"},{"id":"d7b50f36f7","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《香花乎？毒草乎？(1)》（西北师范学院学委会，1957年6月18日）。","index":19,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d"}],"page":{"id":"84e2ae8455","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"324f266d1d","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}